    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 22 },
      "id": 102,
      "title": "Rate Limits & Degradation",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "description": "Rate-Limit-Auslastung: Zeigt RESOURCE_EXHAUSTED Degradation-Events, die auf Rate-Limiting durch externe APIs hinweisen (EPO OPS: 3.5GB/Woche, OpenAIRE/Semantic Scholar: Request-Limits).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "Events",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 80,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "hideFrom": { "legend": false, "tooltip": false, "viz": false },
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "scaleDistribution": { "type": "linear" },
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "normal" },
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "off" }
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 23 },
      "id": 20,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": ["sum"],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "title": "Rate Limit / Resource Exhausted Events",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "sum(increase(uc_degradation_total{error_type=~\"resource_exhausted|timeout\"}[5m])) by (uc_service, error_type)",
          "legendFormat": "{{uc_service}} — {{error_type}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "description": "Gesamte Degradation-Events aller UC-Services nach Fehlertyp. Zeigt die Verteilung von Timeouts, Unavailable, Resource Exhausted und internen Fehlern.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "Events",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 80,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "hideFrom": { "legend": false, "tooltip": false, "viz": false },
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "scaleDistribution": { "type": "linear" },
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "normal" },
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "off" }
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byRegexp", "options": ".*timeout.*" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "orange", "mode": "fixed" } }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byRegexp", "options": ".*unavailable.*" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "red", "mode": "fixed" } }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byRegexp", "options": ".*resource_exhausted.*" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "yellow", "mode": "fixed" } }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 23 },
      "id": 21,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": ["sum"],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "title": "Alle Degradation Events nach Typ",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "sum(increase(uc_degradation_total[5m])) by (error_type)",
          "legendFormat": "{{error_type}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 31 },
      "id": 103,
      "title": "Externe Datenquellen — Referenz",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "description": "Uebersicht der externen Datenquellen und ihrer Rate-Limits",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "text", "value": null }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 32 },
      "id": 30,
      "options": {
        "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false },
        "content": "# Externe Datenquellen — Rate Limits & Hinweise\n\n| Datenquelle | Service | Rate Limit | Hinweise |\n|-------------|---------|------------|----------|\n| **EPO OPS** | Patent-Services (maturity, cpc_flow, patent_grant) | 3.5 GB/Woche, OAuth2 Token | v2 nutzt lokale PostgreSQL-Kopie statt Live-API |\n| **OpenAIRE** | landscape-svc | Optional Token erhoet Limits | Publikationszaehlung, Graph-API |\n| **Semantic Scholar** | research-impact-svc | 100 req/5min (ohne Key) | h-Index, Zitationsdaten, Top Papers |\n| **GLEIF** | competitive-svc | Keine offiziellen Limits | LEI-Lookup, Entity Resolution |\n| **CORDIS** | Diverse UC-Services | Kein API-Key noetig | v2 nutzt lokale PostgreSQL-Kopie |\n\n## Monitoring-Hinweise\n\n- **Rate-Limit-Fehler** erscheinen als `RESOURCE_EXHAUSTED` in den Degradation-Events\n- **Timeouts** koennen auf langsame externe APIs hindeuten (v.a. Semantic Scholar)\n- **UNAVAILABLE** bedeutet, dass der UC-Service selbst nicht erreichbar ist\n- Die meisten Daten werden aus der lokalen PostgreSQL geladen (Bulk-Import)\n- Nur OpenAIRE und Semantic Scholar machen Live-API-Calls pro Anfrage\n\n## v1 vs v2 Architektur\n\n- **v1**: Direkte API-Calls bei jeder Anfrage (SQLite + REST APIs)\n- **v2**: PostgreSQL Bulk-Import + optionale Live-Ergaenzung (OpenAIRE, Semantic Scholar)",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Externe Datenquellen — Rate Limits & Architektur",
      "type": "text"
    }
  ],
